high_descs: Turn around, go forward a step, turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the black stand.
Take the knife from the stand.
Stay at the stand.
Put the knife on the gray plate.
Take the plate from the stand.
Turn around, go forward to the round black table.
Put the plate on the table to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife on it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around, turn right at the door, walk to the small table to the left of the white table.
Pick up the sharp knife from the table.
Look up at the back of the table.
Put the knife on the plate on the back of the table.
Pick up the plate from the table.
Turn around and walk to the black table.
Put the plate down on the black table to the left of the other sharp knife.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife on a plate and put it down on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around, head left towards the door and turn right to reach the small black table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle in the middle of the table.
Look up towards the back of the black table.
Put the knife on the plate with swirls in the back right corner of the table.
Pick up the plate with the knife from the table.
Turn around and walk to the black round table ahead.
Put the plate with the knife on the table to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a knife on a table.
